Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:06.32,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:06.32,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:12.66,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:12.66,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:27.37,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:27.37,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:33.61,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:33.61,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:39.05,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:39.05,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:44.56,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:44.56,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:50.09,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:50.09,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:56.53,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:56.53,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:07.41,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezoro no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:07.41,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:37.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:39.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:40.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:42.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita left it here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:43.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:49.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was wondering what Morita-senpai was trying to do by taking Hagu-chan's footprint...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:52.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, the other day, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:55.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:58.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:01.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:05.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}Help me, Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:05.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:09.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san has been chasing after her quite persistently these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:09.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Stop chasing after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:12.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing it all for his creation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:16.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It only took him two or three days to come up with a new creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But he sure did a great job with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:24.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you apply this kind of skill to your homework, Morita?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:27.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Hagu-chan doing now, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:32.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Morita gave her quite a fright...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:36.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's locked herself in and is now channeling her\Nstress into her new piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:38.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen any of her works.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:53.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:54.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:56.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But be gentle about it, since she's concentrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:58.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what she's making.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:00.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:05.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A magnum opus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:11.59,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38\fscx80\b0\bord2.2\shad0\fnHarting\pos(434,25)\c&H95AEBE&\3c&H4A5867&}Petrified State
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:07.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible concentration, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:12.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't even drink water when she's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:17.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This piece will be displayed in the lobby of a new art museum in Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:23.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of mine who owns a gallery has been looking\Nout for Hagu ever since she entered high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:26.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been asking to "get Hagumi-san's work at all costs."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:30.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:34.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised every time I look at her works as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It just feels like it will come to life any moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Birds, flowers, or people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I often talk with that gallery owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:46.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he'd like to become Hagu just once,\Nto see the world through her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"I wonder what it would look like," he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:52.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That ability to stir such emotions in others...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is probably what talent truly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, even her footprints are pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:17.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan is amazing, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:30.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in... quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I entered college thinking I wanted to accomplish something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:38.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't yet decided what I want to do in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't thought about anything like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:47.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So watching Hagu-chan made me fret a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:51.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's kind of like how Morita-senpai looks like he's doing whatever he wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's actually doing something incredible somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not quite sure about that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:04.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mayama-senpai, after graduation you're also going to work\Nat that store design office you're part-timing at, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At Rika-san's place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not too sure just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:20.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oba-chan, another kakiage, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:21.72,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,0)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Kakiage: {\be1\3c&H000000&}vegetables dipped in batter and deep-fried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:21.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:23.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:29.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a sophomore, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fret and just try something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try out everything that interests you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:39.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of things you can learn easily once you give it a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:48.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to throw a big teppanyaki party sometime next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:48.41,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,0)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Teppanyaki: {\be1\3c&H000000&}food roasted on a hot iron plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We could invite Hagu-chan and the\Nother people from the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good. Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:57.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your noodles are getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I'm digging in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit splashing the soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:11.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:14.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:15.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:22.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:25.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:27.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu's Notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's the list of things you want to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:31.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Mules, bags, dresses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know girls' stuff was so expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to buy all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to cost you a fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:47.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's making this because she can't affort all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:52.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Asahido Bookstores...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Korobokkur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:10.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to see a picture on the internet\Nwhich looked a lot like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On the internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:15.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right here. On this site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:18.34,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\1a&H16&\fs33\fscy70\be1\shad0\frz-12\pos(701,41)\3c&H203130&\c&H4A4DED&}Finally\Ndiscovered!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:20.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:20.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Morita-san's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:22.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the mushroom stool from that other time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And isn't this that footprint from the day before yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san's pushed this a bit too far though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:33.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The banners are scattered all over the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:35.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much he receives for a click.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:41.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,50% of the links lead to ads instead of the next page.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the? 100,000 hits a day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:48.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this site is very popular among the fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:51.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's updated regularly, plus more and more secret\Npages seem to be popping up these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:57.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My guardian angel is Gates Almighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That person's still alive, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say I didn't expect this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:10.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems like he's always running\Ninto money one way or another...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:12.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:19.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:29.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a paperweight of your footprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:32.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure got told.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:01.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... could you please sell that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My footprint paperweight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Owwie...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're hurt, I'll take you to the nurse...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:43.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:57.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:01.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But... what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:14.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a teppanyaki party?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:20.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll invite professor Hanamoto, Hagu-chan\Nand the guys from the apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:23.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out to work again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will you be out for this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably for about a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait for you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:33.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you in a week then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:36.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You better be back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put my money on him not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:47.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yamada Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:55.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto Hagumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-senpai sure is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:27.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really say he was going to be back in a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been nine days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:31.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe his work's holding him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:36.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we just throw the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan's coming too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san may not look like it, but he likes being with people...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:52.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed he was looking forward to it, so he'll be sad if we do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's wait for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:56.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.06,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san likes being with people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.22,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps Takemoto was more mature than I thought he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:23.29,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Mature, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:20.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can I help you, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:25.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:28.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a pair that fits this foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:31.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-One moment please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be these right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:35.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 32,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you pay with a card or...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:43.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm in a hurry, so I'll pay with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:47.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:57.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:14:59.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going smoothly, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:03.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess my introduction paid off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:10.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, one of my relatives is going to our college now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto Hagumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:18.46,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}moshimo kimi ga inaku natteshimattara
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:18.46,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you were ever to disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:20.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:29.64,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}tatoeba neko ya imomushi ni natteshimattara
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:29.64,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you were to become a cat or a caterpillar,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:31.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer is already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:37.15,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}meso meso to naku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:37.15,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I would weep then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're making that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:43.96,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}demo sono uchi tsugou no ii neta ni shiteshimau ka mo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:43.96,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But maybe I would laugh about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:49.99,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}nee dakara kyou wa sou itsumo yori
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:49.99,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, let's talk a lot today,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.90,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}nagai denwa wo shiyou
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.90,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Longer than our usual calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:16:00.67,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}nantonaku kimi ni ushirometai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:16:00.67,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since I somehow feel guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:05.94,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}yasashiku furumatteokou
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:05.94,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be nice to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:18.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess the call was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:21.43,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}moshimo kimi to tomodachi ni natteitara
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:21.43,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we would ever become friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:23.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm doing this right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:28.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:31.64,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}shitta fuu na kao de jogenshitekureta nara
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:31.64,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you could give me an advice with a knowing face...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:44.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when Morita-senpai's coming back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about him already and let's eat some meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seriously lacking calories these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:54.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:00.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto, is the teppanyaki party over yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't started yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:07.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:11.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you brought meat for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:17.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,680 yen per kilo... so you held out for the lowest price, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:18.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:25.24,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they related by a bond of trust by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:27.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:29.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she really hates him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mules!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:15.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the pink laminate mules!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:30.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:33.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mo-Mo-Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan, Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a pair of mules!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:39.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:41.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:19:01.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go back to the apartment and lay him down on a futon for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:06.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't look too well, and he probably\Nwon't wake up for another 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:12.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's throw the party after he wakes up, Mayama-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:14.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:19.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto, you're a really nice guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:23.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after he put you through all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:26.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You kind of remind me of Sabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:27.07,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\b0\be1\fscy80\fs39\fnAlsina Ultrajada\shad0\c&HA8B6DB&\3c&HE5EFF2&\pos(260,42)}Sabu (Faithful Dog)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:27.07,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H84AED2&\bord0\b0\fscy75\fs41\fnAlsina Ultrajada\shad0\pos(264,416)\c&H929C9C&}Akita Breed/4 y.o.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pink mules!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:30.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute little mules!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, Morita got 'em, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:37.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder where he got a hold of such nostalgic sandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:43.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All the delinquent girls used to sport them back in the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's those mules!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much did Morita-senpai pay for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:00.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:04.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should have left the meat in the office refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:09.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, Hagu-chan seemed really happy, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:13.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll forgive you for putting her on your site.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:14.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:18.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Those sandals really looked nice on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:23.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was... really... happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:36.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:37.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:39.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:42.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:48.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:50.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is my stomach hurting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I eat something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:54.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:01.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, he's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:04.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gotten heavier as I slowed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:05.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I better walk faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:08.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten a lot heavier all of a sudden, Morita-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:11.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a konaki-jijii?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:13.85,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,50)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Konaki-jijii: {\be1\3c&H000000&}a Japanese demon, appears as a baby. After being\Npicked up, gradually gains weight and crushes the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:27.83,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}akanai mabuta kosutte mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:27.83,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I rub my heavy eyelids to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:32.94,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}pastel moyou no mirai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:32.94,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}A future in the shape of pastels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.30,0:21:40.08,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}chiribamerareta kigou o tadoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.30,0:21:40.08,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I follow the scattered symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:44.18,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}taguri yoseta hyoujou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:44.18,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}As my expressions were pulled in closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:49.92,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}nee nandakke sagashiteita mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:49.92,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Say, what was it that we were looking for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:53.02,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}are wa soune itsudakke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.45,0:21:53.02,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}That's right, exactly when were those days
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.96,0:22:00.40,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}bokura ga inryoku ni sakarai nagara deatta koro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:22:00.40,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}When we used to meet, denying the attraction\Nthat was forming between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:06.30,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sore ga waltz no you dane fushigi sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:06.30,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}It's like a waltz, isn't it? It's quite marveling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:12.54,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sasayaku youna komorebi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:12.54,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}We paint away sceneries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:18.75,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}futari waltz no youni ne mawari nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:18.75,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}As we waltz and spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:24.89,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}egaki dashite yuku mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:24.89,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}Where the whispering sunlight falls through the trees and meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: They were two unrequited feelings.
